headline: Amcor plc (AMCR) Could Boost Volumes and Margins by 100 Basis Points, Says Jefferies
summary: Amcor plc (NYSE:AMCR) ranks among the best fast growth stocks to buy now. With a price target of $11.67, Jefferies reiterated its Buy rating on Amcor plc (NYSE:AMCR) on September 10. According to the firm, Amcor’s primary categories climbed by low single digits, despite the fact that attitude toward the packaging company has been strained […]
